---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<!-- About page -->
<Layout title="About">
  <Header />
  <main class="p-6 text-gray-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-start h-screen">
    <section class="max-w-5xl space-y-10">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">What is JobFindy?</h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          JobFindy is a platform that aggregates job listings from several sources. Originally created for personal
          needs, it's now available for everyone. We hope it aids you in your job search!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">How does it work?</h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          JobFindy refreshes its listings every 6 hours. With each update, a notification is pushed to our discord
          server. You can join it <a href="https://discord.gg/H2HQhtBect">here</a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Clicking on "Apply" redirects you to the post's original site.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Our Sources</h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">We currently gather listings from:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Reddit</li>
          <li>WeWorkRemotely</li>
          <li>Remotive</li>
          <li>RemoteOK</li>
          <li>JobIcy</li>
          <li>FOSSJobs</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">Use our menu filters to narrow down jobs based on your preferred sources.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold">Future Plans</h1>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          We aim to expand our sources. For now, we've chosen the most accessible sites for scraping.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
